"Crispy savoury balls stuffed with the finest combination of spices, rich 
nuts and wholesome besan. A signature Haldiram's recipe, paired with

items.name: Trikoni Khasta 200Gm
items.description: Savor our Trikoni Khasta, triangular crispy snacks with a savory filling.

items.name: Namkeen Stick 200Gm
items.description: Crispy namkeen sticks, made with the goodness of atta, these biscuits are delicately flavoured with salt and a dash of spices. Serve with spicy minth chutney or a cheese dip 200gms

items.name: Methi Mathri 200 Gm
items.description: Crunchy crackers packed with the delicious aroma of methi and flavourful spices. A signature Haldiram's recipe, methi puris are the perfect addition to your snack jar. 200gms

items.name: Methi Stick
items.description: Wholesome cracker sticks made with the goodness of atta and a dash ofMethi & spices. These crunchy masala sticks are an answer to all your snacking needs! 200gms

items.name: Mini Bhakarwadi 200 Gm
items.description: Delectable bite-sized besan rolls stuffed with delicious sweet and spicy coconut flling. Made with exotic sweet coconut stuffng, enhanced with the flavour of toasted spices, this namkeen is rightfully Maharashtra's flavourite and the perfect snack of your dreams! 200gms

items.name: Mini Samosa 200 Gm
items.description: Reward yourself with these bite-sized, golden triangles stuffed with a spicy, flavourful flling. These miniature version of India's flavourite snack has faky crusts and extra delicious centres. It's an explosion of flavour waiting to happen! 200gms

items.name: Namkeen Karela 200Gm
items.description: Enjoy the unique taste of our Namkeen Karela, crispy bitter gourd chips with a spicy twist.

items.name: Jeera Puri 200 Gm
items.description: Savor our Jeera Puri, crunchy puris with a cumin taste that are ideal as a snack.

items.name: Salted Kaju 35 Gm
items.description: Deliciously crunchy, premium cashews that have been perfectly salted.
